patthana16.74:1.1_0: Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ ajjhattikaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho naajjhattiko
patthana16.74:1.1_1: dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ ajjhattikaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nasanidassanasappaṭigho
patthana16.74:1.1_2: naajjhattiko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā …pe… anidassanaappaṭighaṁ ajjhattikaṁ dhammaṁ
patthana16.74:1.1_3: paṭicca nasanidassanasappaṭigho naajjhattiko ca naanidassanasappaṭigho naajjhattiko
patthana16.74:1.1_4: ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā cha. Ārammaṇe tīṇi …pe… avigate cha.
patthana16.74:2.1: Anidassanasappaṭighaṁ bāhiraṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nasanidassanasappaṭigho nabāhiro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā ekādasa, ārammaṇe tīṇi …pe… avigate ekādasa.
